Hw6: Textures and Lighting

Zhanchao Yang
CSCI4229 Fall 2022

To compile files, do "make",to open it,do "./hw6"
"
Note that lighting part from hw5, not much change, Texture image from ex14/ex15, using five of these pictures (water, block, crate, image 3/6), write my comment with understanding why use these gl functions. Operation, key function is modify from ex15/hw5, change most value and remove some useless key.

Time to complete: 4 hours

Key bindings
  l          Toggle lighting on/off
  t          Change textures(have 2 different combinations texture)
  p          Toggles texture mode modulate/replace
  m          light movement
  a/A        decrease/increase ambient light
  d/D        decrease/increase diffuse light
  s/S        decrease/increase specular light
  e/E        decrease/increase emitted light
  n/N        Decrease/increase shininess
  u/U        Lower/rise light
  x          Toggle axes
arrows(Up,down,left,right)     Change view angle
  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit
